### 통계검정 {.unnumbered}


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(infer)


# 관측통계량
observed_indep_statistic <- penguins %>% 
  specify(species ~ island) %>%
  hypothesize(null = "independence") %>%
  calculate(stat = "Chisq")

# 통계검정 시각화
penguins %>% 
  specify(species ~ island) %>%
  assume(distribution = "Chisq") %>% 
  visualize() + 
  shade_p_value(observed_indep_statistic,
                direction = "greater")  
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](penguins_analytics_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-1.png){width=672}
:::

```{.r .cell-code}

# P값
penguins %>% 
  specify(species ~ island) %>%
  assume(distribution = "Chisq") %>% 
  get_p_value(obs_stat = observed_indep_statistic,
              direction = "two-sided")
#> # A tibble: 1 × 1
#>   p_value
#>     <dbl>
#> 1       0
```
:::


:::

다른 `species`와 `sex`, `sex`와 `island` 범주 사이는 특별한 관계를 찾을 수 없음.

::: {layout-ncol=2 .column-page}

### `species`와 `sex` {.unnumbered}


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(janitor)
library(gt)

penguins %>% 
  count(species, sex) %>% 
  pivot_wider(names_from = sex, values_from = n, values_fill = 0) %>% 
  adorn_totals("row", name = "합계") %>%
  adorn_percentages("row") %>%
  adorn_pct_formatting(digits = 1) %>%
  adorn_ns()  %>% 
  gt::gt() %>% 
  tab_options(table.font.names = 'NanumGothic',
                column_labels.font.weight = 'bold',
                heading.title.font.size = 14,
                heading.subtitle.font.size = 14,
                table.font.color = 'steelblue',
                source_notes.font.size = 10,
                #source_notes.
                table.font.size = 14) %>%   
    gtExtras::gt_theme_538()
```

